What’s GOLDTRON Smart Contract all about ?
GoldTron is Open source smart contract uploaded to Tron Block-chain. Cryptocurrency is international and decentralized. Instant payouts, cheating excluded. Money is not stored in the system. All transactions are automatically...100% Decentralized. Automated And Amplified Power by Tron Block-chain. Instant Wallet-to-Wallet Money Transfers
GoldTron is a fully automated, decentralized, and smart Contract Platform. It is designed and created exclusively for maximising stakeholders' TRX reserves. The entire code of this Platform is written on a self-executing smart contract, which is governed by predefined conditions and compensates the benefits of network marketing activities that the stakeholders perform on this platform
Who Owns  this Program?
Since GOLDTRON is built on a self-executing smart contract, there will be no admins or management or owners to this platform. Whoever participates in this program, will become stakeholders of the program and it is their duty and right to promote it for their own good.
