*Do The Matrix Or Level Expire.?*

NO. The Matrix do not expire. Once all the positions of the current Matrix are filled, the same Matrix reopens, at the same time you will also have a chance to upgrade yourself to the next Matrix

Suppose you are in Matrix 1 of plan GM2 and once you successfully filled all the Six positions of that Matrix, two things will happen:

*Matrix 1 reopens again*
You will get a chance to upgrade to the next Matrix
You can repeat the same Matrix any number of times and you can operate more than one Matrix at the same time.
What of If I bring more Downline than required to that particular Level?

If all the positions of your present Matrix are filled, the same Matrix reopens, and your additional downlines automatically fills up the empty positions of the reopened Matrix.
What of I bring more Downline than required to that particular Level

What of if i cannot bring enough Downlines requires to complete all Positions of a level

Your profitability from GOLDTRON depends on your network marketing efforts, that is your ability to bring more people to the platform. If, unfortunately, you could not bring enough downlines required to fill empty positions of your current level, the GOLDTRON  Team will help you to move forward.

There are options like * SPILLOVERS and OVERTAKES.*

Spillovers happen when the system fills your empty positions with members. They come either from your uplines or downlines. The code decides who goes where randomly on its own. This happens only for Member’s in GM3-GM4.

Overtakes happen when your partner's downline fills your positions, because your downline has not upgraded to his position. He/she fills your position because you are in the same level as this overtaking downline is in.

Suppose you are in Matrix 2 and one of your downlines in Matrix 1 has not upgraded himself to Matrix 2 but his downline upgrade himself to Matrix 2. Now since his immediate upline is not in Matrix 2, he falls under your empty position since you are in Matrix 2.
SO. Though the structure represents the matrix/pyramid model, GOLDTRON SMART CONTRACT is fundamentally different from Others in many aspects like:
It has no admins or managers to control or manipulate the system, all investors act as its stakeholders and promoters.
The system holds no funds at all, every transaction is peer-to-peer.
It is very transparent and securely built on TRON's smart contract technology.
It is completely self-governed and can run eternally.
It has no hidden fees, commissions, and charges
